l=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118050456/https://www.wenweipo.com/a/202101/13/AP5ffe34f9e4b0553aff396028.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，香港《[[大公报|大公报]]》认为，邓小平的思想贯穿了整部香港基本法的修订过程，其有关“爱国者治港”的论述所反映的是基本法立法原意<ref>{{cite news |author1=社评 |title=重温邓公谈话坚持爱国爱港 |url=http://news.eastday.com/eastday/news/node4472/node4511/node4823/userobject1ai82894.html |accessdate=2021-03-11 |work=香港大公报 |publisher=东方网 |date=2004-02-20 |archive-date=2021-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313031013/http://news.eastday.com/eastday/news/node4472/node4511/node4823/userobject1ai82894.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

